Interface SinglebandKernelProcessor.Processable<T,S extends Image<T,S>,I extends Image<?,I>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The pixel type that is processed
    S - The image type of the underlying single band images
    I - The image type that is processed
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FImage, MBFImage, MultiBandImage, SingleBandImage
    Enclosing interface:
    SinglebandKernelProcessor<T,I extends Image<T,I>>

    public static interface SinglebandKernelProcessor.Processable<T,S extends Image<T,S>,I extends Image<?,I>>
    Interfaces for objects that allow themselves to be processed by a SinglebandKernelProcessor.
